---
import PublicLayout from '../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Book a free consultation call with Smagile, or get in touch to discuss how we can help your teams."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">Get in touch</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-grey-700 dark:text-grey-300">
      Whether you have a specific challenge in mind or just want to explore how we might work together,
      we would love to hear from you.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 p-8 bg-grey-50 dark:bg-grey-800 rounded-xl border border-grey-200 dark:border-grey-700">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">Book a free consultation call</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-grey-700 dark:text-grey-300">
        A no-obligation conversation to understand your challenges and discuss how Smagile can help.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@smagile.co"
          class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors"
        >
          Email us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 p-8 bg-grey-50 dark:bg-grey-800 rounded-xl border border-grey-200 dark:border-grey-700">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">Remote retrospective facilitation</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-grey-700 dark:text-grey-300">
        Need an independent facilitator for your team's retrospective? We run remote sessions
        that create space for honest, productive reflection.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@smagile.co?subject=Retrospective%20Facilitation"
          class="inline-block px-6 py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary dark:border-secondary dark:text-secondary hover:bg-primary hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-secondary dark:hover:text-grey-900 font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors"
        >
          Enquire about facilitation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
